      $( Lemma for ~ cvgrati .  A complex infinite series ` F ` meeting the
         ratio test criterion converges.  We show that the partial sums of
         ` F ` are smaller than the partial sums of a geometric series (which
         converges by ~ geolimi ), so by the comparison test ~ cvgcmp3ce ,
         ` F ` also converges. $)
      cvgratlem5 $p |- ( ( ( A e. RR /\ A < 1 ) /\ ( B e. NN /\
           A. x e. NN ( B <_ x ->
  ( abs ` ( F ` ( x + 1 ) ) ) < ( A x. ( abs ` ( F ` x ) ) ) ) ) ) ->
                    E. y ( + seq1 F ) ~~> y ) $=
